snippet.textDisplay:
On one hand, it is slightly hilarious that the entire internet decided to hivemind and only respond to this video with various forms and lengths of "wah." On the other hand, it is simultaneously extremely stupid and frustrating that I cannot find any actual discussion on this video because everyone is merely typing "wah." And people are massively downvoting any response that isn't "wah" which is also just further shutting down any meaning conversations, such as:


What was that operatic music near the end from? Was he mimicing/referencing some famous movie?
Just HOW fabulous is BDG? Can it even be measured?


But we don't get conversations. We don't even get the normal hilarious jokes in the comments I normally can find in the comments. This makes me sad.


Wah.
